com.djrapitops.plugin.logging

Class FolderTimeStampFileLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.djrapitops.plugin.logging.FolderTimeStampFileLogger
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FolderTimeStampErrorFileLogger, FolderTimeStampFileDebugLogger

    public class FolderTimeStampFileLogger
extends Object
    Logging utility class that is used to log messages into files with timestamps.

    This class is used by other logger classes and creating instances is not required.
